For create autodeploy, necessary :

**** install last version apache-maven https://maven.apache.org/download.cgi
**** install tomcat http://tomcat.apache.org/

**** setting path in environment variables, e.g.:
	- MAVEN_HOME / E:\DEV\Maven\apache-maven-3.5.0
	- MAVEN / %MAVEN_HOME%\bin

**** add in pom.xml:

	- tomcat7-maven-plugin (<groupId>org.apache.tomcat.maven</groupId>)
	- configuration: 
		url - http://localhost:8080/manager/text, create name server, username, pass, path
		!!! add update - true (<update>true</update>)

**** add in tomcat-user.xml:
	- role rolename  manager-script / manager-gui
	- user username and pass

**** add in setings.xml (apache-maven-3.X.X/conf/)
	- activeProfiles (if you used more two profiles)

------------------------------------------
root cmd command 
------------------------------------------
create deploy: 
	- mvn tomcat7:deploy
checking active profiles created by â pom.xml
	- mvn help:active-profiles
run / stop tomcat:
	- startup.bat / shutdown.bat
delete all artefact, target directory
	- mvn clean
delete and create new target directory with new war
	- mvn clean install
chek of work maven
	-mvn –version

